<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>bed head • sleepy head</xh5><p> <i>bed head</i>—(sl.) the way one’s hair looks after sleeping on it: The only time my hair is curly is when I have a <u>bed head</u>.</p><p><i>sleepy head</i>—(coll.) a sleepy or lethargic person: I will give Laura a big hug as soon as she’s awake. She really is a <u>sleepy head</u>.</p> </entry>
